NAME
    Alien::Ditaa - Use the ditaa text to diagram package in perl

SYNOPSIS
        use Alien::Ditaa;
        my $ditaa = Alien::Ditaa->new;
        $ditaa->run_ditaa(@args);

DESCRIPTION
    Trivial wrapper to run ditaa from perl.

SEE ALSO
    <http://ditaa.sourceforge.net>

